OL,4,G1245FOutback Truckers
OL,5,     GOver the last three days, Steve
OL,6,     GGrahame has hauled 130 tonnes of
OL,7,     Gfreight a massive 2000 km, and
OL,8,     Ghis truck's taken a beating.
OL,9,     GUnder the bonnet the news isn't
OL,10,     Ggood.
OL,11,G1345FOutback Truckers
OL,12,     GA driver travels through an area
OL,13,     Gwhere bush fire has run wild. An
OL,14,     Gowner operator faces the busiest
OL,15,     Gweek of his career.
OL,16,G1440FOutback Truckers
OL,17,     GTurbo gambles his truck and his
OL,18,     Glife to complete an epic journey
OL,19,     Ghome. Plus, logging trucker Brett
OL,20,     Ghas a battle on his hands to
OL,21,     Gdeliver some huge machines deep
OL,22,     Ginto a mountain forest.
